<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lembrete de Atividade - <%= companyName %></title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; background-color: #0d1117; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #c9d1d9; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background-color: #161b22; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #30363d; }
        .header { background: #f59e0b; padding: 20px; color: #000; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 30px; line-height: 1.6; }
        .activity-box { background: #0d1117; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .footer { padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; color: #8b949e; border-top: 1px solid #30363d; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: #6366f1; color: #fff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2 style="margin:0">⏰ Lembrete de Atividade</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Olá, <strong><%= userName %></strong>!</p>
            <p>Você possui uma atividade agendada para daqui a pouco no <strong><%= companyName %></strong>.</p>
            
            <div class="activity-box">
                <p style="margin:0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #f1f5f9;"><%= activityTitle %></p>
                <p style="margin:5px 0 0; color: #f59e0b;">Vence às: <%= dueDate %></p>
            </div>

            <p>Prepare-se para o atendimento e boa sorte!</p>
            
            <a href="<%= crmDashboardUrl %>" class="btn">Acessar Pipeline</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> <%= companyName %> · Automação NexusAI</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>